The LibArchive library is downloaded as a submodule.
In order to get it, run "git submodule init" after cloning.

See also:
https://git-scm.com/book/en/v2/Git-Tools-Submodules

To compile, just run the script "builtTest.sh". This will (if neccessary) compile libarchive, and then compile&run the tests (static and dynamic linking).